Output assets/screenshot.png

Set Width 800
Set Height 480
Set FontSize 22
Set FontFamily "monospace"
Set LetterSpacing 0
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 15
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set WindowBarSize 40
Set TypingSpeed 1ms

Hide
Env PS1 "$ "
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Type "typefully --help"
Enter
Sleep 1s
Show
Sleep 500ms

Screenshot assets/screenshot.png
